sentences: Previously he was known as a named partner at the Waxman Leavell Literary Agency.
In 2012, he partnered with Scott Waxman to form the Waxman Leavell Literary Agency.
In September 2017 he began his employment at UTA.
Haddish's memoir, The Last Black Unicorn, was a debut New York Times bestseller, spending each of its first six weeks in print on the list and, as of January 2018, reaching #5 overall.
